1
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:23,959
The river is long,

2
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:25,959
and the river is endless.

3
00:01:28,719 --> 00:01:31,840
The smoke of war rises high.

4
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:35,879
The galaxy is far away,

5
00:01:36,519 --> 00:01:37,400
but the galaxy is also a wish.

6
00:01:39,040 --> 00:01:41,400
The blue sky is a sign of peace.

7
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,840
I finally found you.

8
00:01:48,599 --> 00:01:49,400
Wei'an.

9
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:57,879
How did you find me?

10
00:02:00,439 --> 00:02:01,480
It's Wei'an.

11
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:04,359
Oh.

12
00:02:04,719 --> 00:02:05,640
It's Xu Mengxi.

13
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:07,599
He gave himself away too much.

14
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:12,439
Only Wei'an knew I love sweets

15
00:02:13,039 --> 00:02:14,120
and sugar cakes.

16
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:18,680
Only Wei'an knew where the battle bear king was.

17
00:02:20,319 --> 00:02:21,199
Only Wei'an

18
00:02:21,759 --> 00:02:23,879
knew the song of Wangchuan.

19
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:27,240
I should have realized it earlier.

20
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:31,759
That kind of warm and honest words

21
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:33,759
only belong to you.

22
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,039
I'm sorry.

23
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:37,599
It took me

24
00:02:38,439 --> 00:02:39,479
so long to find you.

25
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:44,560
I'm the one who should apologize.

26
00:02:47,319 --> 00:02:48,360
I actually

27
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:50,800
wanted to tell you a long time ago

28
00:02:51,039 --> 00:02:52,000
that I am Wei'an.

29
00:02:53,479 --> 00:02:54,240
But I couldn't.

30
00:02:56,080 --> 00:02:58,120
I can't fulfill your wish now.

31
00:03:00,159 --> 00:03:01,199
I can't write anymore.

32
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:04,719
It's been nine years.

33
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,360
I can't write a single character.

34
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:09,479
I'm sorry.

35
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:12,039
I was too cowardly.

36
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,639
Everyone

37
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:16,919
has moments of cowardice.

38
00:03:17,919 --> 00:03:18,919
That's not scary.

39
00:03:20,599 --> 00:03:22,439
Only those who can accept their own cowardice

40
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:25,199
can become stronger.

41
00:03:25,759 --> 00:03:26,560
This sentence

42
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:28,840
was written by you in Galaxy Chronicle.

43
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:30,759
Now,

44
00:03:31,319 --> 00:03:32,560
I give it back to you.

45
00:03:33,479 --> 00:03:35,400
But I lost Galaxy Chronicle.

46
00:03:37,159 --> 00:03:39,199
Galaxy Chronicle was accused of plagiarism

47
00:03:39,759 --> 00:03:40,400
and cyberbullying.

48
00:03:42,919 --> 00:03:46,199
I was crushed by the accusations and insults.

49
00:03:48,039 --> 00:03:49,719
Later, my brother stopped him.

50
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:51,479
He protected me.

51
00:03:52,199 --> 00:03:54,039
He said he was Wei'an.

52
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:57,280
But after that,

53
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:58,960
I was trapped

54
00:03:59,439 --> 00:04:01,560
in another cage.

55
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:05,159
After that, no matter what I wrote,

56
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:07,879
I couldn't prove that it was my writing,

57
00:04:07,879 --> 00:04:08,800
not his.

58
00:04:10,599 --> 00:04:11,240
After that,

59
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:16,959
I didn't know how to be myself.

60
00:04:18,639 --> 00:04:19,439
or even

61
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:24,800
I can't write anymore.

62
00:04:39,639 --> 00:04:41,120
I am your writing.

63
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,079
Look at me.

64
00:04:45,399 --> 00:04:46,439
I like sweet cakes

65
00:04:47,519 --> 00:04:48,759
because you do.

66
00:04:49,199 --> 00:04:50,480
I love the people of Qingyun Sect

67
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:53,800
because you do.

68
00:04:54,959 --> 00:04:56,519
I can overcome the setbacks

69
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:58,839
because

70
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:00,319
you've already

71
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,480
overcome them.

72
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:08,360
You don't need to prove anything to anyone.

73
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:09,839
Who is Wei'an?

74
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,120
Because

75
00:05:13,319 --> 00:05:14,120
your words

76
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,120
will prove it for you.

77
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,360
Wake up.

78
00:05:29,839 --> 00:05:30,920
It's getting dark.

79
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:31,920
Go home and sleep.

80
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,040
Wait.

81
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,079
There's a surprise.

82
00:05:45,639 --> 00:05:47,480
There's no surprise that's spoken out loud.

83
00:05:53,199 --> 00:05:53,879
Here.

84
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,439
Silly brother.

85
00:06:07,319 --> 00:06:07,920
Happy birthday.

86
00:06:13,839 --> 00:06:15,000
Xu Chi's birthday is coming.

87
00:06:15,199 --> 00:06:17,079
How about we make him a birthday cake together?

88
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:18,319
What are you doing?

89
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:19,959
When beating the egg,

90
00:06:19,959 --> 00:06:21,040
you need to apply even force.

91
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:21,560
Oh.

92
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:22,319
Have you learned it?

93
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:24,000
This way, it will gradually start to foam up.

94
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,120
In the end, it will...

95
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:27,639
So you two are being all lovey-dovey

96
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,199
just to make this?

97
00:06:29,319 --> 00:06:31,040
What do you mean by lovey-dovey?

98
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:33,240
Xu Mengxi said we are

99
00:06:33,519 --> 00:06:35,240
strategic partner.

100
00:06:36,759 --> 00:06:37,160
Oh,

101
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:39,519
he asked you to save him a piece.

102
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,319
He'll be here soon.

103
00:06:40,839 --> 00:06:41,480
No,

104
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:42,839
I'll eat it all.

105
00:06:43,199 --> 00:06:44,000
Wait,

106
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:46,160
in your world,

107
00:06:46,279 --> 00:06:48,279
do you make a wish

108
00:06:48,279 --> 00:06:49,040
before eating cake?

109
00:06:49,879 --> 00:06:50,639
Make a wish.

110
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:52,560
Okay.

111
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:02,600
Don't open your eyes.

112
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:08,040
Done.

113
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:15,600
They say red ropes come in pairs.

114
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,040
Happy Birthday.

115
00:07:18,079 --> 00:07:18,480
Wei'an.

116
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:23,439
Brother, let's go home.

117
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,959
Here's your ball, thanks.

118
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:25,720
Okay.

119
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:33,680
Wei'an.

120
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,519
What kind of ending

121
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:38,160
will you give to Galaxy Chronicle?

122
00:07:40,079 --> 00:07:41,120
I'll give you a new life.

123
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,040
Not just you,

124
00:07:43,839 --> 00:07:44,639
but also Xiao Chengjing.

125
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:46,680
He won't betray you.

126
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:50,040
He still has a soft spot in his heart.

127
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:51,600
That's your

128
00:07:51,839 --> 00:07:53,279
deep bond.

129
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,800
You are the twin stars in chaos.

130
00:07:56,519 --> 00:07:57,439
The war began with you

131
00:07:58,480 --> 00:07:59,319
and ended with you.

132
00:08:00,959 --> 00:08:01,720
From now on,

133
00:08:02,319 --> 00:08:03,879
Qingyun Country will be in peace.

134
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,199
What about me?

135
00:08:12,879 --> 00:08:13,800
What's my ending?

136
00:08:14,519 --> 00:08:16,160
I hope you can be yourself

137
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:19,519
and have the right to choose your own destiny.

138
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:28,000
Yan Ying,

139
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:30,079
I'm not God.

140
00:08:31,839 --> 00:08:34,080
I can't even control my own destiny.

141
00:08:35,159 --> 00:08:36,000
I have my own selfishness.

142
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,320
My selfishness is that

143
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:42,600
I hope you can stay in my world.

144
00:08:45,759 --> 00:08:47,120
How can I write it?

145
00:08:48,759 --> 00:08:50,360
I'm afraid that once the ending is changed, you will...

146
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:01,159
This is a gamble.

147
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,240
But if you're the stake,

148
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:06,799
I can't bet.

149
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,679
Then let's

150
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,000
make a bet.

151
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:19,799
If I make this shot,

152
00:09:21,679 --> 00:09:22,440
you'll bet.

153
00:09:48,679 --> 00:09:49,440
Bet.

154
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:50,759
Be brave.

155
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,399
Yan Ying.

156
00:10:17,799 --> 00:10:19,039
The galaxy falls.

157
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,279
The blood moon

158
00:10:23,039 --> 00:10:23,720
reappears.

159
00:10:25,039 --> 00:10:26,200
The twin stars will fall.
